<lb n="5"/><unclear>to</unclear>ṇṇūṟṟu Añciṉmel cellāniṉṟa paritāpa va<hi rend="grantha">rṣa</hi>m Āṉi mātam
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="11" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p><hi rend="italic">Line 6 to 14 are very much damaged.</hi></p>

<p>
<lb n="15"/>ku meṟkum Āka Ivvellaikkuṭpaṭṭa nancai puncaikku Ūrviṉiyokam Āḷamañci <unclear>meṟ</unclear>
<lb n="16"/>ce <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> kaḻittu tamakkum tamvarkkattārukkum cantirātittavaraiyum celvatāka veṭṭik ku
